examples.en: The gas tank has a capacity of 12 gallons.
He took on board some 3,000 gallons of wine.
We were rationed to ten gallons of gasoline a month.
Gallons of water cascaded over the side of the bath.
Standard washing machines use about 40 gallons of water.
The damaged ship disgorged thousands of gallons of oil into the bay.
The factory secretly dumped millions of gallons of raw sewage (=that had not been treated) into the Ohio river.
